'''飓风奥拉夫'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Olaf}}）是2003年10月上旬以飓风下限强度吹袭墨西哥的太平洋飓风，于10月2日经[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南偏南方向的[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成。经过组织，东风波于次日发展成热带低气压，并且仅六小时后就升级成热带风暴并获名“奥拉夫”。气旋继续增强，于10月5日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时120公里的最高强度，属一级飓风，同时还发展出局部[[风眼|风眼墙]]。

风暴结构很快就变得混乱，只在飓风强度下保持六小时，然后就回转逼近墨西哥海岸。10月7日，奥拉夫从[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]并迅速消散，虽在[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]和[[瓜纳华托州|瓜纳华托州]]引发严重洪灾，但并未造成人员丧生。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Olaf 2003 track.png}}
9月17日，有东风波离开非洲西海岸进入大西洋，并在接下来两星期里向西移动，直至进入东太平洋<ref name="OlafTCR" />。外界环境起初不利于东风波发展<ref name="TWO">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233145/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200310022226 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200310022226 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | author1 = John Brown | author2 = Lawrence | date = 2010-10-02 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>，但10月2日的[[卫星影像|卫星图像]]却显示系统内已存在下层环流。接下来数小时里，环流在墨西哥[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]以南约645公里海域快速组织<ref name="OlafTCR">{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | work = National Hurricane Center | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Olaf | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152003_Olaf.pdf | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | date =  | archive-date = 2016-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161222044043/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152003_Olaf.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。次日，气象机构采用[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]估算得出的数值为1.5，表明气旋分速在每小时50公里左右，同时还有系统附近的船只测得每小时45公里风速，微波图像也表明气旋中心位于关联的对流附近。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]根据这些信息将系统归类成热带低气压。<ref name="Disc 1">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Eighteen-E Discussion 1 | last = Franklin | date = 2010-10-03 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160326043034/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-26 | accessdate = 2016-08-24 }}</ref>

由于[[2003年飓风诺拉|飓风诺拉]]就在左近，气象部门预计新生的热带低气压会因诺拉产生的[[风切变|风切变]]而减弱，但气旋实际却很快升级成热带风暴并获名“奥拉夫”（{{lang|en|Olaf}}）<ref name="Disc 2">{{cite report | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Olaf Discussion 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325051802/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.002.shtml | author = Franklin | year = 2003 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | archivedate = 2016-03-25 | date =  }}</ref>。风暴朝西北方向前进并稳步增强，于10月3日晚达到中等热带风暴强度。次日，奥拉夫略有减弱，<ref name="OlafTCR" />但很快又得以强化，约24小时后就成为强烈热带风暴<ref name=OlafTCR />。气象机构此时指出，风暴有可能继续强化<ref name="Disc 7">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.007.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Olaf Discussion 7 | last = Jarrvien | date = 2003-10-04 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322170338/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | accessdate = 2016-08-24 }}</ref>。10月5日，雷达图像表明气旋内存在局部[[风眼|风眼墙]]，气象部门因此把热带风暴升级成飓风，奥拉夫也在几乎同一时间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]120公里，最低[[气压|气压]]987[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）的最高强度。奥拉夫在飓风强度下仅保持约六小时<ref name="OlafTCR" />，但美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中认为风暴的中心位置比实际更偏北侧，与深层对流的距离更近，并且在飓风强度下保持的时间也要长得多<ref name="Disc 13">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160319220015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.013.shtml? | title = Hurricane Olaf Discussion 13 | last = Franklin | date = 2010-10-06 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-24 }}</ref>。

达到最高强度后不久，气旋结构就变得混乱。风暴稳步减弱，移动速度也逐渐放缓。到了10月6日清晨，回转向西北方向前进的奥拉夫强度已降至热带风暴下限。<ref name="OlafTCR" />但气旋这天下午快速组织，气象机构经评估认定其风速又提升至每小时80公里<ref name="Disc 15">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322115323/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.015.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep152003.discus.015.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Olaf Discussion 15 | last = Franklin | date = 2003-10-06 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-22 }}</ref>。奥拉夫此后还有进一步强化，于10月8日以风力时速97公里强度从墨西哥[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]附近登陆。此后不久，风暴在沿海地区的高原上空迅速减弱，登陆不到24小时后就在内陆上空消散。<ref name="OlafTCR" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Olaf-Nora2003filledrainblk.gif|thumb]]的降水分布]]

奥拉夫达到最高强度时，[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]蓬塔圣特尔莫（{{lang|en|Punta San Telmo}}）到[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，蓬塔圣特尔莫到圣布拉斯（{{lang|en|San Blas}}）和[[玛丽亚群岛|玛丽亚群岛]]接获飓风观察预警。此外，曼萨尼约到圣布拉斯间地区和玛丽亚群岛之后又进入飓风警告生效状态。三小时后，由于风暴实际强度远低于预期，上述飓风警告和观察预警随即中止，但热带风暴警告持续生效到10月7日。<ref name="OlafTCR" />米却肯州、[[科利马州|科利马州]]和[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]进入黄色预警生效状态，[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]、[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]、[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]和[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]则收到绿色预警<ref name="PHNO">{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-02-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120227004931/http://www2.eluniversal.com.mx/pls/impreso/noticia.html?id_nota=15231&tabla=primera | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/175348.html | title = Alerta en el Pacífico por huracanes Olaf y Nora | date = 2003-10-06 | publisher = OffGuard | accessdate = 2016-08-24 }}</ref>，各地有关部门还开设有避难所<ref name="MPHO">{{cite web | title = Mexicans prepare for hurricane Olaf | last = Staff Writer | date = 2003-10-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140116121531/http://noticias.terra.com/noticias/mexico_se_prepara_por_huracan_olaf_mientras_larry_se_debilita/act163047 | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | archivedate = 2014-01-16 | deadurl = no | url = http://noticias.terra.com/noticias/mexico_se_prepara_por_huracan_olaf_mientras_larry_se_debilita/act163047 }}</ref>。

2003年的墨西哥雨量充沛<ref name="OlafTCR" />，其中奥拉夫产生的降水比飓风诺拉还多<ref name="Roth">{{cite web | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/noraolaf2003.html | title = Hurricanes Nora/Olaf - October 3–8, 2003 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | author = David M. Roth | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090623/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/noraolaf2003.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。虽然风暴没有造成人员遇难，但引发的洪灾还是导致哈利斯科州许多道路和庄稼严重受损，该州还有1万2000余套民房受损<ref name="OlafTCR" />。[[瓜纳华托州|瓜纳华托州]]估计有1万5000人受到洪灾影响，另外还有两个社区同外界的交通中断。飓风过去后，当地需要的捐赠物资包括食品和基本家居用品。<ref name="PHA">{{cite web | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-post-hurricane-flooding-appeal-no-2203 | title = Post-hurricane appeal | last = Staff Writer | date = 2003-06-23 | publisher = Reliefweb | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | archivedate = 2016-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160824131952/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-post-hurricane-flooding-appeal-no-2203 | deadurl = no }}</ref>诺拉和奥拉夫的残留湿气同上层低气压区相互影响，令[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]普降暴雨，[[韦科_(得克萨斯州)|韦科]]附近发生洪灾，[[麦格雷戈_(德克萨斯州)|麦格雷戈]]（{{lang|en|McGregor}}）有一户人家被迫撤离。受洪灾影响，[[35号州际公路德克萨斯州段|35号州际公路]]、[[84号美国国道|84号国道]]和[[德克萨斯州36号州道|36号州道]]部分路段封闭<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Beaumont Enterprise | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 2003-10-09 | title = Possible tornado hits Houston suburb; floods hit Waco area | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160610144649/http://www.beaumontenterprise.com/default/article/Possible-tornado-hits-Houston-suburb-floods-hit-761124.php | archivedate = 2016-06-10 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | url = http://www.beaumontenterprise.com/default/article/Possible-tornado-hits-Houston-suburb-floods-hit-761124.php }}</ref>。此外，天气系统还在[[舒格兰_(得克萨斯州)|舒格兰]]催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，致使四幢楼房受到破坏，其中还包括一所学校<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Reading Eagle | date = 2003-10-11 | title = Tornadoes Hit Part of Texas | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V1sxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EqMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3575,5864549&dq=tropical+nora&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701064852/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V1sxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EqMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3575,5864549&dq=tropical+nora&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

